description:
Mama's Little Girl (5 pages)

Sharon gets married to Jim but has trouble living away from her mother.

Too Beautiful (5 pages)

Karen Starr, a successful model, runs into Tony Evans at an art gallery. They fall in love, but when he realizes she is a successful model they almost split up. She asks him to marry her and agrees to his conditions, that she quit her job and move out of her Park Avenue apartment so that he can support her on his writer's salary.

One of the Finest (5 pages)

Dan, a police detective, spots a crook when he is on his honeymoon and gets involved in arresting him.

It Had to Be You (5 pages)

Elaine Darby starts working for Steve Turner, a Hollywood executive. They fall in love and he asks her to marry him.

A Tragic Evening (2 pages)

Mona gets asked to a formal party by Bill but doesn't have a dress to wear.
name: Mama's Little Girl

description:
Born Jealous

Ever since I was a little girl, I had felt lonely and unloved! My parents had been killed in an auto accident when I was just a baby! Consequently I had lived with my Aunt for almost as long as I can remember! When the time came for me to be a woman, I desperately wanted a love of my own! But when I found it, I became my own worst enemy! I made Tom's life miserable... it was as though I had been... Born Jealous

The Proposal

The marriage proposal is a custom as old as civilization! Most of us think of it as the man being on bended knee, asking for the girls hand in marriage...

Once Too Often

Dick and I had known each other ever since we were kids! I guess I had loved him even as a little girl! And there were times when I thought he loved me! I still believe he did! But sometimes there's something in a person that makes them hold back! They'll go only so far, then they run away from love! Such was the case with Dick! And each time he would tempt me, I would charge blindly ahead with the hope that this may be it! Finally, he broke my heart... Once Too Often

Marriage

Marriage is the most exciting thing that can happen to a girl! At last she ha found the right boy, and the whole world opens up for her...

Martha Marsden Meditates (Text Only Story)

Meeting Place For Lovers

When I went away for that weekend, I had no idea that I would return home with Cupid's arrow through my heart! But it happened, and I could hardly believe it! Vince was everything I could have hoped for in a boy! Those two days were the most ecstatic, fulfilling I had ever known, and the thrill of them had swept me off my feet! Love seemed to be all that filled my mind! But I was soon to learn that love also brings problems which must be ironed out if that love is to survive...
name: Born Jealous; The Proposal; Once Too Often; Marriage; Martha Marsden Meditates; Meeting Place For Lovers

description:
Tragic Love

Bob and I were dizzily in love! Since the first moment we met, it was undeniable! And this despite the fact that we did not know each other very long before we were married! So the events that followed were as startling and sudden as the way we had fallen in love! And through it all there was Jim, quiet, outgoing, but never speaking his true thoughts! Not even at the crucial moment... because he knew that the future was not up to him... it was completely in my hands... if I could only find the strength to face it...

Bride of the Year

At first, I couldn't believe it was happening... out of hundreds of wives in Oak Hill Knoll, the judges had chosen me as bride-of-the-year! Then, when I thought it over... I knew it was only ust that I be chosen... because hadn't I done a wonderful job on our home?.. and, yes... hadn't I transformed Bob too into a successful advertising executive instead of the happy-go-lucky ambitionless fellow he'd been when he married me?

Painful Lesson

It took a painful lesson to teach me that two people in love have to give a little. my selfishness cost me a boy I really cared for...

Find That Girl (Text Only Story)

Model of Misbehavior

Why couldn't Ray understand I was doing it for him? So many of our friends in the Village earned extra money by modeling for painters like Dik Maas... but my husband had forbidden me to do it... and now... he had caught me in the notorious artist's studio!
name: Tragic Love; Bride of the Year; Painful Lesson; Find That Girl; Model of Misbehavior

description:
A Dream Come True and Was Almost A Nightmare

As Reverend Cutshaw said those beautiful words "I now pronounce you man and wife" my heart almost stopped... and I turned to take Don's first kiss as a husband! Down deep I still couldn't believe that this wondrous thing was really happening to me... it was a fantastic dream I'd cherished since childhood... when his lips touched mine... would I awaken once again to harsh reality?

Putting On Pressure (Text Only Story)

Perfect Marriage

We'd entertained out friends Saturday night... and all our friends congratulated me time after time on what a perfect hostess I made! Leo's male friends kept staring at me and my husband told me later "he punctuated the compliments with kisses" that I'd looked absolutely ravishing! Next morning, I got quietly out of bed and cleaned the entire house... then I cooked a huge breakfast with all Leo's favorite dishes and brought it in to him... along with the Sunday paper of course!

When True Love Came

This should've been the happiest moment of my life... Bob and I were man and wife at last... we were in that luxury hotel I'd always wanted to see... and there was only one flaw! All of a sudden... I didn't love my husband!
name: A Dream Come True and Was Almost A Nightmare; Putting On Pressure; Perfect Marriage; When True Love Came

description:
I'm Not the One For Him

Vikki and I have been friends since Kindergarten... friendly rivals, of course... but she's gayer, prettier, and far more sophisticated that I! She's always snared the handsomest boys, naturally... and I never cared until now! Ray Tomlin has just moved to town... he's a lawyer in Vikki's uncle's law firm... and he's earmarked for her!

A Gentle Man to Love

All my friends are amazed when they see me with Arnold Lundegan, the squarest man in town. I'm a swinger, see... I've been way way out... and this non-cat figures to be straight from Main Street. Dullsville, U.S.A. Sure I know the I.B.M. operators wouldn't pick our cards, but I know what I want... a tender, loving man who'll always be there when I need him...

Time of Beauty

Before this part given by Lee's company president, my husband warned me about Adam Munson ...the company Casanova, he's said... and sure enough the moment Lew went for champagne cocktails, Adam arrived by my side!
name: I'm Not the One For Him; A Gentle Man to Love; Time of Beauty
